strings.Value: "The fate of Varnhold haunts me. I pray its people are unharmed."
"My prayers fly with yours. Been thinking about those people, too. Don't want it to end as it did with my village. Would that we can help..."
"Alas, these are the Stolen Lands. Time and again people disappear here without a trace, whole groups, and even whole settlements."
